node.text:
Experience the best of life below the surface through the lens of a #GoPro. What's your all-time favorite? 

🔟 Exploring the Bahamas with #GoProFamily member @andremusgrove 🤿
9️⃣ #GoProAwards recipient @mathieuvillegas going below the surface of a frozen lake 🧊 
8️⃣ Observing the chaos of a sardine run with #GoProAwards recipient @expert.tours 🎣
7️⃣ Swimming in sharky waters with #GoProFamily member @abc4explore 🦈
6️⃣ Arctic Bear Productions sharing the sea with a family of polar bears 🐻‍❄️
5️⃣ Saving the turtles with @camerondietrich 🐢
4️⃣ #GoProFamily member @brinkleydavies takes us down under on the west side 🇦🇺 
3️⃣ Once in a lifetime whale diving with @deepleigh, @mandyraekrack, + Erin Magee 🐋
2️⃣ @orcaingrid + @orcaresearchtrust freeing an Orca whale caught in a fishing buoy 🐳
1️⃣ Surrounded by a million fish with William Mitchell 🤯

#UnderwaterPhotography #Sharks #NaturePhotography #Whales #Dolphins #MarineLife #Top10

node.text:
Empowered by a global community, we've shared over 2,000 stories since 2009. From sobering reminders of humans' impact on this planet to seemingly impossible moments caught on camera, the content has stacked nearly 3 billion views + over 10,000 years of watch time—inspiring heroism + celebrating creative expression.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
What is your favorite #GoPro video? Let us know below. 👇 Over the next 10 hours, 10 lucky comments will take home a #GoProHERO9 Black.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Hour 1: @gheeohm 👉 Getting the Shot - B.C. Backcountry in 4K 🏆
Hour 2: @mister.adrians 👉 Coast Guard Rescues Sinking Yacht 🏆
Hour 3: @flip821 👉 Fastest Hydroplane on Earth 🏆
Hour 4: @themoooose_ 👉 Freerunning Santorini 🏆
Hour 5: @janelle.vanhalteren 👉 Rémy Métailler Taxco Downhill 🏆
Hour 6: @_amysimms_ 👉 Chasing AdVANture with Chris Benchetler 🏆
Hour 7: @ahlabinho 👉 Airplane Failure Marriage Proposal 🏆
Hour 8: @heyitsaishah 👉 Great Barrier Reef in 4K 🏆
Hour 9: @dillanjimenezc 👉 Freediving with Tiger Sharks in 4K🏆
Hour 10: @nickfaestel 👉 Puppy Mashup🏆
